Detailed Description

This structure defines BAR parameters.

These parameters are used for configuring BAR window

Field Documentation

pcieBarAddrSize_t pcieBarParams::barAddrSize

BAR address size 32 or 64 bit Values given by enum pcieBarAddrSize_t

pcieBarType_t pcieBarParams::barType

BAR is memory or IO type Values given by enum pcieBarType_t

uint32_t pcieBarParams::enableBar

Enable or disable BAR

uint32_t pcieBarParams::enablePrefetch

Enable pre-fetch Usually this is enabled for memory transactions and disabled for IO and configuration access

uint32_t pcieBarParams::lowerBarMask

BAR mask to configure lower BAR window

uint32_t pcieBarParams::lowerBaseAddr

BAR lower address

uint32_t pcieBarParams::upperBarMask

BAR mask to configure upper BAR window for 64 bit BAR Not used for 32 bit BAR

uint32_t pcieBarParams::upperBaseAddr

BAR Upper address used for 64 bit BAR. Not used for 32 bit BAR
